    "name": "Shyftrs",
    "steam_appid": 1899120,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/eee878bc6d0a3ae0db1c88a9927f846d.avif?t=1767503282\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras_big/eee878bc6d0a3ae0db1c88a9927f846d.avif?t=1767503282 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>一个瑰丽而险恶的世界，待你揭晓</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Shyftrs》是一款2D手绘风格的类银河战士恶魔城冒险游戏，你的每一步，都将揭露地表之下潜藏的另一个世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演声名显赫的探险世家科尔文家族的后裔——布拉姆斯・科尔文。父母在秘密远征中离奇失踪，而你追寻真相的旅程却意外打破了现实疆界，将你从埃索斯抛入光怪陆离的伊卡洛斯王国。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索遗忘废墟，唤醒失落科技，穿梭于现实与幻象交织的星界。<br>在这片遗忘之神与禁忌科学并存之地开辟你的道路，揭开血脉中那不该被触碰的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你将重返埃索斯……抑或让伊卡洛斯永远重塑你的命运？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔥 核心特色</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 <strong>风格化手绘美术</strong><br>所有角色、生物与场景皆为画师亲手绘制，打造出一个笔触细腻又栩栩如生的世界。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌍 <strong>相互连结的广大领域</strong><br>穿梭于伊卡洛斯与星界两个维度，此处充满了秘密、隐藏路径与蕴藏丰富传说的场景。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ <strong>动态组合的战斗系统</strong><br>自由组合在探索、头目战、制作与支线任务中解锁的技能，打造专属于你的战斗风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧩 <strong>暗影之中，皆有秘密</strong><br>在这个鼓励探索、奖励好奇心的世界中，发掘隐藏密室，解锁稀有遗物，并揭开被遗忘的真相。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐉 <strong>超过百种独特敌人</strong><br>你将面对种类繁多的敌人，包括扭曲的不死生物、源于神话与疯狂的奇异魔物等。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎶 <strong>原创配乐与场景设计</strong><br>沉浸感十足的原创配乐，结合视差滚动的精致背景，为每个生态区注入了独特的氛围与故事深度，使其活灵活现。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">星界探索</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>启动钥石，即可在主世界与星界之间来回穿梭</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/9c33e94322b388672a1a596239cb2e14.poster.avif?t=1767503282\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/9c33e94322b388672a1a596239cb2e14.webm?t=1767503282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/9c33e94322b388672a1a596239cb2e14.mp4?t=1767503282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/6b72e759be05858ac1dba5870c20ce4b.poster.avif?t=1767503282\" width=700 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/6b72e759be05858ac1dba5870c20ce4b.webm?t=1767503282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/6b72e759be05858ac1dba5870c20ce4b.mp4?t=1767503282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >星界包含：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 可供探索的全新关卡设计。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 全新的敌人与头目</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 全新的隐藏宝藏与遗物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>星界敌人</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/378f00d6081024f9b41ad5c9b2d84854.poster.avif?t=1767503282\" width=800 height=343 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/378f00d6081024f9b41ad5c9b2d84854.webm?t=1767503282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/1390b1107ecedd12ec5c681b88debc1e.avif?t=1767503282\" width=1084 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/36c53b2476986b379a69d176f3f887a3.poster.avif?t=1767503282\" width=800 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/36c53b2476986b379a69d176f3f887a3.webm?t=1767503282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/36c53b2476986b379a69d176f3f887a3.mp4?t=1767503282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得新的技能与能力，克服重重阻碍，向更深处探索。找出隐藏路径，自由应对所有挑战——你的创造力将会决定这趟旅程的面貌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/00fe714bd77c6cecd103e469d05fc2e4.poster.avif?t=1767503282\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/00fe714bd77c6cecd103e469d05fc2e4.webm?t=1767503282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/00fe714bd77c6cecd103e469d05fc2e4.mp4?t=1767503282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伊卡洛斯的亚丁王国将是游戏的主要舞台，这是一片魔力丰沛的土地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此地包含着互相连结的广大生态网络，每个区域都拥有其独特的动植物生态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/de5297fe8063e4374c6da2ac81131a91.avif?t=1767503282\" width=600 height=700 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>欢迎造访我们的网站，在「更新／博客」专区查看游戏的重大更新与未来规划。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/c5736d1b5c29e86b8810b683523a9a98.poster.avif?t=1767503282\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/c5736d1b5c29e86b8810b683523a9a98.webm?t=1767503282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/c5736d1b5c29e86b8810b683523a9a98.mp4?t=1767503282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/6377d006adafd9801baa9b81c2420ede.avif?t=1767503282\" width=600 height=211 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>开发资助</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们团队孜孜不倦，致力将《Shyftrs》付诸实现。我们的首要目标是取得初期资金以加速开发。在此荣幸宣布，我们已成功获得<strong>CODE NZ</strong>的支持，分别于<strong>2022年12月</strong>与<strong>2024年8月</strong>两度获得资助。<br>我们由衷感谢CODE NZ团队的持续指导，以及对《Shyftrs》愿景的信任。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899120/extras/6c8837519c5753686c94069e2882cac5.avif?t=1767503282\" width=400 height=76 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Discord:  / X: @shyftrs / Bluesky: </strong></h2>",
